body_html: I think the underlying issue here is that you need to specify the right input and output names when you call transform_graph too. In the code above, you're using the default of Mul and final_result when you invoke the tool, but they should be input and MobileNet/Predictions/Softmax, like your application code.

body: I think the underlying issue here is that you need to specify the right input and output names when you call `transform_graph` too. In the code above, you're using the default of `Mul` and `final_result` when you invoke the tool, but they should be `input` and `MobileNet/Predictions/Softmax`, like your application code.
